subroutine init_como_log(subroutineName)
* turn on como logging and log some basic information

{% include "../../common/mvom.njk" %}

* hush must be off so that all terminal output is captured
hush off
execute 'COMO APPEND ':S$MVOM.COMO.LOG.KEY
crt subroutineName
crt S$MVOM.REQUEST.ID
crt oconv(date(), 'd4/')
crt oconv(system(12) / 1000, 'mts')

return
